## PLAN COLORS — import from lib/constants/planColors

Never hardcode plan color hex values in components.
Always use PLAN_COLORS[plan.color].border / .bg / .accent / .glow etc.

Available keys: red, blue, yellow, green, purple, orange

Each key provides: label, border, bg, bgStrong, chip, chipBorder, chipText, accent, accentHover, glow

Set as CSS custom properties on the plan root element:
- --plan-accent
- --plan-accent-hover
- --plan-border
- --plan-bg
- --plan-bg-strong
- --plan-chip
- --plan-chip-border
- --plan-chip-text
- --plan-glow
- --plan-tint
- --plan-tint-strong
- --plan-card-glow

