## SKELETON LOADING

- Always use class skeleton-shimmer from globals.css
- Never recreate shimmer animation inline
- Use skeleton-card for card-shaped placeholders
- Page-level skeletons live in components/shared/skeletons/
- Show skeleton when TanStack Query isLoading is true
- Swap entire content area for skeleton — never conditional inline skeletons except for detail panels loaded after click

